dcterms:description: The ABCD Consortium dataset provides structural brain imaging data from a large cohort of adolescents around 10 years old, allowing for the analysis of the association between intelligence and cortical thickness.
dcterms:title: Adolescent Brain and Cognitive Development (ABCD) Consortium

dcterms:description: The NIH Toolbox Cognition Battery (NIHTB-CB) includes composite scores of crystallized, fluid, and overall cognition, providing a standardized measure of cognitive abilities in children and adults.
dcterms:title: NIH Toolbox Cognition Battery (NIHTB-CB)
